  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Start of Your Turn] If a Digimon card with [Unidentified]
    in its type is in your trash, gain 1 memory.[Your Turn] When one of your Digimon
    digivolves into [Diaboromon], you may suspend this Tamer to play 1 [Diaboromon]
    Token without paying its memory cost. (Diaboromon Tokens are level 6 white Digimon
    with a memory cost of 14, 3000 DP, and are Mega form, Unidentified type, and
    Unknown attribute.)'
